ed="T" n="0776a13"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0776a13"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012402"><placeName>明州</placeName><placeName>大梅山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010512">法常</persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2655"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0776a14"/><persName key="A010512">釋法常</persName>，俗姓<name>鄭</name>，<placeName key="PL000000027119">襄陽</placeName>人也。稚歲從師於<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊</placeName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0776a15"/><placeName key="PL000000027023">玉泉寺</placeName>。凡百經書，一覽必暗誦，更無遺忘。<date key="j20026622003026" from-iso="+0771-01-01" to-iso="+0771-12-31">冠<lb
ed="T" n="0776a16"/>年</date>，受具足品於<placeName key="PL000000027846">龍興寺</placeName>。容貌清峻，性度剛敏，<lb
ed="T" n="0776a17"/>納衣囊鉢，畢志卯齋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1764"/>。<date from-iso="+0796-02-18" key="j20118412012194" to-iso="+0797-02-05"><name>貞元</name>十二年</date>，自<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0776a18"/>之于<placeName key="PL000000012277">四明</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012470">餘姚</placeName>之南七十里，寓<persName key="A006905"><persName>仙尉</persName><persName>梅子真</persName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0776a19"/>之舊隱焉。昔<persName key="A006905">梅福</persName>初入山也，見多龍穴，神<lb
ed="T" n="0776a20"/>蛇每吐氣成樓閣，雲雨晦冥。邊有石庫，內<lb
ed="T" n="0776a21"/>貯仙藥神仙經籍。<persName key="A010512">常</persName>寄宿于房，乃夢神人語<lb
ed="T" n="0776a22"/>之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010512">君</ref>非凡夫。」因話及石庫中聖書懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/><lb
ed="T" n="0776a23"/>既往將來之事，受之者為地下主，不然為<lb
ed="T" n="0776a24"/>帝王之師傅矣。<persName key="A010512">常</persName>謂之曰：「石庫之書，非<ref type="person" target="#A010512">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0776a25"/>所好。昔<persName key="A004688">僧稠</persName>不顧仙經，其卷自亡<ptr target="#n2656"/>。<ref type="person" target="#A010512">吾</ref>以涅<lb
ed="T" n="0776a26"/>槃為樂，厥壽何止與天偕老<anchor xml:id="beg0776001"/>耶<anchor xml:id="end0776001"/>？」神曰：「此地<lb
ed="T" n="0776a27"/>靈府，俗氣之人輒難居此，立致變怪。」<persName key="A010512">常</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0776a28"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A010512">吾</ref>寓跡於<persName key="A006905">梅</persName>尉之鄉，非久據焉。」因號<placeName key="PL000000012402">梅山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0776a29"/>也。由是編<anchor xml:id="beg0776sgsz5"/>苫<anchor xml:id="end0776sgsz5"/>伐木，作覆形之調，居僅四十<pb ed="T" n="0776b" xml:id="T50.2061.0776b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0776b01"/>年，驗實非常之人也。<date notBefore-iso="+0836-01-26" key="j20264282026797" notAfter-iso="+0837-01-29"><name>開成</name>年初</date>院成，徒侶<lb
ed="T" n="0776b02"/>輻湊，請問決疑，可六七百納<anchor xml:id="beg0776sgsz6"/>徒<anchor xml:id="end0776sgsz6"/>矣。<date from-iso="+0839-01-23" key="j20275212027904" to-iso="+0840-02-10">四年</date>，<persName key="A010512">常</persName>忽<lb
ed="T" n="0776b03"/>示疾。<date key="j20278042027804" when-iso="+0839-11-02">九月十九日</date>，山林搖盪，鳥獸悲鳴，辭眾<lb
ed="T" n="0776b04"/>而逝，報齡八十八，戒臘六十九。<date key="j20278342027834" when-iso="+0839-12-02">十月十九日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0776b05"/>焚于南㵎，收舍利，五色璨然圓轉焉。<persName key="A010512">常</persName>先<lb
ed="T" n="0776b06"/>隱<placeName key="PL000000012402">梅嶺</placeName>，有僧求拄杖見之<ptr target="#n2657"/>，白<placeName key="PL000000012856">鹽官</placeName><persName key="A003862">安<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0776b07"/>曰：「梅子熟矣，汝曹往尋，幸能療渴也。」進士<lb
ed="T" n="0776b08"/><persName key="A010514">江積</persName><ptr target="#n1567"/>為碑云爾。</p>
